{"tid":1244829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】民陣再促撤銷暴動定議 胡志偉：掟磚改控普通襲擊","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T06:24:13.000Z","uid":29270,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67083097d33c51761f3350dbd1a1d9e2129b2368","tid":1244829,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰今日再次要求當局撤銷暴動定義，撤回對示威者的控罪。民主黨立法會議員胡志偉也認為，青年因涉嫌投擲磚塊等行為被捕，警方可改控普通襲擊等罪名。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有大專學界學生會要求政府在今日內回應遊行市民的訴求，否則明日會在政府總部外發起集會。岑子杰早上出席一電台節目時指出，一旦學界發起包圍政總行動，民陣願意參與。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的胡志偉特別提醒學生及參與的市民，明日一旦包圍政總時，要保持和平，因擔心太偏激的行為，會令民意逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1527034/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1527034%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=da4a4a86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1527034%2F&h=85c9995f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1527034/</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"b5789fd509e068bc85fe96e2edf7f0d7319a55c5","tid":1244829,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8c81235d178641301d1e367a6e3d36e80d67939b","tid":1244829,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"大台又篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db6f009eeae06d482a6892d0371ec6a9d734f3","tid":1244829,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明日一旦包圍政總時，要保持和平，因擔心太偏激的行為，會令民意逆轉。</blockquote><br />\n圍住政總唱毅進校歌<img src=\"/assets/fac